### 1. Register a new musician
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "guitarist@example.com",
  "password": "supersecretpassword"
}

### 2. Log in to get the JWT
# (Copy the "access_token" string from the response)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "guitarist@example.com",
  "password": "supersecretpassword"
}

### 3. Post a new Jam Event 
# (Replace <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE> with the actual token you copied)
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "title": "Tuesday Bachata Social",
  "eventDate": "2026-03-17T20:00:00Z",
  "location": "Caracas Center",
  "description": "Weekly bachata dancing! All levels welcome."
}

### 4. Post an acoustic jam session
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "title": "Acoustic Guitar & Coffee Jam",
  "eventDate": "2026-03-21T10:00:00Z",
  "location": "El Hatillo",
  "description": "Bring your acoustic and let's jam over some good coffee."
}